    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. It runs smoothly, looks great, and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner! I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you'll love how it drives just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 31500.0,
