    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW 5 Series is the perfect blend of luxury and performance, maintained with care and ready for its next owner. The exterior features a classic Alpine White finish that retains a high gloss; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving, the body is straight and free of any significant dents. It sits on factory alloy wheels wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of Black Dakota leather. The seats are firm and supportive with no rips or thinning, and the dashboard remains pristine with all digital displays and ambient lighting functioning as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound. It has received regular synthetic oil changes and recent brake service, ensuring a smooth, responsive ride. The transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears, and the engine runs quietly without any leaks or warning lights. Included are both key fobs, the original owner's manuals, and a clean title. This is a solid, reliable luxury sedan that looks and drives beautifully.",
